The paper deals with algorithms for generating and enumerating sets of vertices and edges in graphs, which are fundamental topics in computer science. The use of graph theory and combinatorics suggests that the paper may belong to the categories of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), Graph Theory (cs.GT), and Computational Complexity (cs.CC).
